| Layer            | Technology                    |
| ---------------- | ----------------------------- |
| Backend API      | ASP.NET Core Web API (latest) |
| Frontend         | Angular 16 or React           |
| Database         | SQL Server with EF Core       |
| Realtime Support | SignalR (for live updates)    |
| Location/GPS     | Google Maps API / Leaflet     |
| Authentication   | ASP.NET Identity + JWT        |
| Hosting          | Azure / AWS (optional)        |
